{"tid":589403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中東人=蝀","createTime":"2018-03-12T00:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T03:16:52.000Z","uid":18323,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a08fab786a045b41dcfb7ad60b61ea63a56f32d2","tid":589403,"uid":18323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:22:24.000Z","msg":"英國澳洲街頭偷呃拐騙嘅十個九個都係中東人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nATM咁完錢 可以厚面皮即刻響你隔離問可唔可以比啲錢嚟洗吓<br />\n人又懶到出汁 uni做group project 外國讀u嘅巴絲應該知咩事<br />\n淨係識搞鳩人哋國家 搞恐襲 炒石油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有錢嘅都係揮霍無度 好食懶非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歷史上都冇出現過對地球有貢獻嘅中東人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蝀係咪地球上最大毒瘤<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7c1926286bed6e81ffd0964c5968c01a1ae946","tid":589403,"uid":49392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:26:30.000Z","msg":"要錢?問揸超跑果班同鄉啦"},{"pid":"8ebe45e19020641d97ed0411792da5d98f08a79f","tid":589403,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:11:24.000Z","msg":"蝻同中東係同種 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d445e07a7063e6631f8dd8a0c27988458c34612f","tid":589403,"uid":80647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:16:02.000Z","msg":"又咸濕,又懶,又唔文明,最叻就係瘋狂生仔,霸佔社會資源"},{"pid":"87d541f537f49ca06f9c850b009a5a658e27e86d","tid":589403,"uid":60831,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:35:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蝻同中東係同種 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不用分那麼細，都係啡皮狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ffdf890ea5130b58fccd181b486fcb0229976d3","tid":589403,"uid":18323,"like":0,"di